source.name: ENERGY STAR Qualified Residential Clothes Washers
source.description: Residential Clothes Washers that have earned the ENERGY STAR are more efficient and use less water than standard models. ENERGY STAR is the trusted symbol for energy efficiency helping consumers save money and protect the environment through energy-efficient products and practices.  More information on ENERGY STAR is available at http://www.energystar.gov.
